{
  "page": "Lord of the Stepstones",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord of the Stepstones</b> was a title conferred on <a href=\"/index.php/Drazenko_Rogare\" title=\"Drazenko Rogare\">Drazenko Rogare</a> by his wife, <a href=\"/index.php/Aliandra_Martell\" title=\"Aliandra Martell\">Aliandra Martell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Princess_of_Dorne\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Princess of Dorne\">Princess of Dorne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The title refers to the island chain called the <a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Stepstones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Stepstones_and_the_Narrow_Sea\" title=\"King of the Stepstones and the Narrow Sea\">King of the Stepstones and the Narrow Sea</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_of_the_Stepstones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw